text: Palko or Palkó is an Eastern European surname and male given name. Notable people with this name include: * Christian Palko , better known as Cage (rapper) (born 1973), American rapper and actor * Dávid Palkó (born 1989), Hungarian football player * Franz Xaver Palko (1724-1767), Silesian painter * Fruzsina Palkó (born 1992), Hungarian handball player * Jiří Palko (1941–2014), Czech rower * Palkó Dárdai (born 1999), German-Hungarian football player * Tyler Palko (born 1983), American football player * Vladimír Palko (born 1957), Slovak politician
